<%=
content_tag(:div, 
	content_tag(:span, "", 
		:class => "ui-icon ui-icon-closethick warning_close", 
		:style => "display:inline-block;",
		:onclick => "$('#manual_species_mapping_help').hide('slow');"
	) +		
	content_tag(:normal,
		"<p>In order to plot intron gain and loss events onto the phylogenetic tree, GenePainter requires a mapping between gene names (FASTA headers) and species names.</p><p>Enter species name or select it from the autocompletion dropdown and select the corresponding gene name(s) from the list next to the input field. Click 'Save' to save the mapping between current species and selected genes. You can then proceed with the next species.</p>You can make changes to the species mapping in the 'Unlink genes from species' menu on the right.".html_safe,
	),
	:id => "manual_species_mapping_help",
	:class => "help",
	:style => "display:none;"
)
%>